members.description: Power On Self Test (POST)/UEFI errors occurred during server restart.

eventDetails.eventItemValue: Refer to the Integrated Management Log for details on the Power On Self Test (POST)/UEFI error.

One or more POST/UEFI errors occurred. Power On Self-Test (POST) errors occur during the server restart process. UEFI errors occur during server boot time and run time. Details of the POST/UEFI error messages can be found in Integrated Management Log.
